Developing a Generalized accouting software for fintech

Requirements 

---General Requirements---

1. Software should be simple to use
2. Software should have aesthetic Interface
3. Software should be upgradable
4. Structure should be modular
5. Compatible with other Tools used in Finance
6. Able to be hosted and used as SaaS
7. should contain all related features and functions used in finance 
8. Cost efficient
9. Security Mechanism
10.Free trial System

---User Side---

    Robust reporting tools
    Ability to customize reports
    Unlimited invoicing
    Tools to assist with automations
    Inventory tracking in some of the plans
    Bill management and receipt capture
    Calculate sales tax automatically
    Accept credit cards and bank orders
    Track projects, including labor costs, expenses, and payroll on some plans

